title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre less likely to think about price and more about quality today. You may wish to spend your money in ways that beautify and enhance your life. Buy a colorful bouquet of flowers to put on your desk to remind you of natures magic. Or, consider purchasing an outfit that increases your sense of self-esteem. For the moment, set aside budgetary limits and let your mind explore the possibilities. Obviously, your self-worth extends beyond your bank account. Shifting your perspective changes your world and enables you to create beauty inside and out. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
